Overview
========

**dothost** is a DNS lookup utility,
which produces output in Graphviz_ format.

.. _Graphviz: https://www.graphviz.org/

Example
-------

.. code:: console

   $ dothost www.iana.org | graph-easy --as boxart

          ┌─────────────────────────┐
          ∨                         │
        ┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓     ┌────────────┐
     ┌> ┃   www.iana.org    ┃ ──> │ 192.0.32.8 │
     │  ┗━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┛     └────────────┘
     │    │
     │    │
     │    ∨
     │  ┌───────────────────┐
     └─ │ 2620:0:2d0:200::8 │
        └───────────────────┘

